summary: Sebastian (@hangarcat)​ proposed during our photo op with David Tennant!!!! It was so sweet and I’m so happy!!! I don’t remember...
caption: Sebastian (@hangarcat)​ proposed during our photo op with David Tennant!!!! It was so sweet and I’m so happy!!! I don’t remember much, mainly just turning around and seeing him down on one knee lol. Apparently David gave me a hug but I was too focused on Sebastian and the ring. Luckily @blogging-molly was there filming so there’s a record of it! Major thanks to her and Steve for helping Sebastian get this planned and making this the best moment of my life!

summary: Cold Vengeance and Zygon Hunt to be Released on Limited Edition Vinyl
title: Cold Vengeance and Zygon Hunt to be Released on Limited Edition Vinyl
body:
Cold Vengeance and Zygon Hunt to be Released on Limited Edition Vinyl

Two limited edition vinyl titles from Big Finish will be released next month, exclusive to Sainsbury’s and HMV.

Doctor Who: Cold Vengeance, starring David Tennant and Billie Piper, will be available from 5th October 2018, and will be the second Big Finish vinyl that Rose Tyler has appeared in following her debut in Infamy of the Zaross earlier this year. You’ll be able to find limited quantities…
